INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'Adidas',41,50,'AH2430.png','2020-04-13 15:06:28','Women\'s adidas Originals NMD_Racer Primeknit Shoes',14999000,'Singapore','Channeling the streamlined look of an \'80s racer, these shoes are updated with modern features. The foot-hugging adidas Primeknit upper offers a soft, breathable feel. The Boost midsole provides responsive comfort accented with a contrast-color EVA heel plug. Embroidered details add a distinctive finish.','Woman'),(2,'Adidas',16,50,'EG0000.png','2020-04-13 15:06:28','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Response Trail Shoes',7999000,'Singapore','When the road turns to trail, all that matters is what lies ahead. These running shoes deliver a plush ride and confident grip in a fresh, sporty look. Cloudfoam cushioning feels ultra-soft while the aggressive outsole grabs on in all directions. The multilayer upper and sleek 3-Stripes elevate your look when you get back to town.','Men'),(3,'Adidas',48,40,'EE9798.png','2020-04-13 15:06:29','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Run 70s Shoes',5599000,'Singapore','These running-inspired shoes are designed with a mesh upper and a textile lining for flexible, all-day comfort. 3-Stripes and a rubber outsole give the shoes a stylish sign-off.','Men'),(4,'Adidas',89,50,'CL4156.png','2020-04-13 15:06:29','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Drogo Shoes',2699000,'Singapore','The adidas running-inspired shoes for men. An excellent combination of breathable Mesh with synthetic overlays on the upper makes it very comfortable for your feet on the run. Durable and non slippery one piece super grip EVA midsole and outsole ensures maximum stability and grip on the ground.','Men'),(5,'Adidas',39,40,'EE9797.png','2020-04-13 15:06:29','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Run 70s Shoes',5599000,'Singapore','These running-inspired shoes are designed with a mesh upper and a textile lining for flexible, all-day comfort. 3-Stripes and a rubber outsole give the shoes a stylish sign-off.','Men'),(6,'Adidas',98,60,'CI9914.png','2020-04-13 15:06:30','Men\'s adidas Running Nayo 1.0 shoes',4999000,'Singapore','The adidas Nayo 1.0 shoes for men. These lightweight running shoes give all round comfort, cushioning, durability & support in a simplistic design. The mesh upper ensure breathability and durability while the Light strike EVA midsole provides premium cushioning\'s. Full Rubber outsole provides durability.','Men'),(7,'Adidas',6,50,'EE8252.png','2020-04-13 15:06:31','Men\'s adidas Sports Inspired Lite Racer Shoes',4299000,'Singapore','The ultra-lightweight build of these shoes takes a running-inspired style to the streets. The sporty look has a breathable and durable mesh upper with stitched-on 3-Stripes. EVA cushioning provides lightweight comfort for every step.','Men'),(8,'Adidas',17,50,'CK9664.png','2020-04-13 15:06:31','Men\'s adidas Running Nepton 2.0 Shoes',5999000,'Singapore','Sleek design with reflective three stripes makes it a contemporary yet functional shoe. Breathable textile upper for maximum ventilation and a cushioned midsole provides all-day comfort with rubber outsole for best durability in high wear areas.','Men'),(9,'Adidas',17,50,'CL7602.png','2020-04-13 15:06:32','Men\'s adidas Running Torik Shoes',4799000,'Singapore','A well cushioned shoe with a fresher look that will appeal to young runners. Features Mesh upper for maximum ventilation, lightstrike IMEVA midsole with visible adiprene providing protection from harmful impact forces and durable Rubber outsole for long-lasting wear.','Men'),(10,'Adidas',28,50,'CL7494.png','2020-04-13 15:06:32','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Kalus 1.0 Shoes',4599000,'Singapore','A well cushioned running-inspired shoes with a fresher look that will appeal to all. Features Mesh upper for maximum ventilation, lightstrike IMEVA midsole with visible adiprene providing protection from harmful impact forces and durable Rubber outsole for long-lasting wear.','Men'),(11,'Adidas',88,40,'EE7923.png','2020-04-13 15:06:40','Men\'s adidas Running Duramo 9 Shoes',5999000,'Singapore','These men\'s running shoes will get you on the road to your goals. A sandwich mesh upper offers lightweight breathability, while a seamless print overlay adds support for a stable stride. The midsole offers pillow-soft Cloudfoam cushioning that eases every stride.','Men'),(12,'Adidas',8,50,'CI1821.png','2020-04-13 15:06:41','MEN\'S adidas RUNNING YAMO 1.0 SHOES',4799000,'Singapore','The adidas Yamo 1.0 shoes for men. These lightweight running shoes have a combination of Synthetic with double layer Mesh ensure breathability and durability while the Lightstrike EVA midsole provides premium cushionings. Full Rubber outsole provides durability.','Men'),(13,'Adidas',64,50,'CJ0082.png','2020-04-13 15:06:41','men\'s ADIDAS RUNNING NEBULAR 1.0 SHOES',4599000,'Singapore','The premium looking adidas Nebular 1.0 Running shoes for men crafted with Mesh overlays which make it lightweight. The breathable sandwich Mesh offer extended ventilation and comfort. Light strike IMEVA midsole with full Rubber outsole provides durability.','Men'),(14,'Adidas',52,50,'CJ8062.png','2020-04-13 15:06:41','MEN\'S ADIDAS RUNNING LEGUS SHOES',5999000,'Singapore','Get maximum support, comfort and a refreshed look with these adidas Legus shoes for men. The textile mesh upper is breathable and has a sock-like fit and the supportive cage in the shoe\'s midfoot provides midfoot lockdown. CLOUDFOAM gives instant step in-comfort, long-lasting responsive cushioning and a super-plush feel and the Rubber outsole gives ultimate durability.','Men'),(15,'Adidas',59,40,'CM0068.png','2020-04-13 15:06:41','Men\'s adidas Toe Side II Slippers',1299000,'Singapore','The adidas casual sandals for men with a striking camouflage design. Features stylish webbing straps, Diecut EVA midsole for stable cushioning and abrasion resistant rubber outsole with wet and dry traction pattern.','Men'),(16,'Adidas',2,50,'CJ0080.png','2020-04-13 15:06:41','men\'s ADIDAS RUNNING NEBULAR 1.0 SHOES',4599000,'Singapore','The premium looking adidas Nebular 1.0 Running shoes for men crafted with Mesh overlays which make it lightweight. The breathable sandwich Mesh offer extended ventilation and comfort. Light strike IMEVA midsole with full Rubber outsole provides durability.','Men'),(17,'Adidas',6,50,'B75579.png','2020-04-13 15:06:45','Men\'s adidas Sport Inspired Duramo Lite 2.0 Shoes',4999000,'Singapore','Refine your interval training in these men\'s versatile running-inspired shoes. Featuring a lightweight mesh and synthetic upper, they combine responsive midsole cushioning with a soft collar that reduces ankle pressure.','Men'),(18,'Adidas',46,40,'CM0057.png','2020-04-13 15:06:49','Men\'s adidas Swim Ozor III Slippers',1299000,'Singapore','The simple and stylish adidas Ozor III slippers for men. Best suited to match with your swimwear, these printed slippers have a soft footbed for additional comfort for your feet while the Synthetic strap with vents provides breathability proper fitting.','Men'),(19,'Adidas',9,50,'CL0206.png','2020-04-13 15:06:49','Men\'s adidas Swim Gadi Slippers',1499000,'Singapore','These thongs are primed for warm-weather fun in a simple design with an urban inspired city graphic print on footbed and adidas brading featured on heel and strap.','Men'),(20,'Adidas',87,50,'CJ8058.png','2020-04-13 15:06:49','MEN\'S ADIDAS RUNNING LEGUS SHOES',5999000,'Singapore','Get maximum support, comfort and a refreshed look with these adidas Legus shoes for men. The textile mesh upper is breathable and has a sock-like fit and the supportive cage in the shoe\'s midfoot provides midfoot lockdown. CLOUDFOAM gives instant step in-comfort, long-lasting responsive cushioning and a super-plush feel and the Rubber outsole gives ultimate durability.','Men'),(21,'Adidas',87,50,'CJ8117.png','2020-04-13 15:06:49','MEN\'S ADIDAS RUNNING HELKIN 3.0 SHOES',4599000,'Singapore','Style and performance go hand in hand in this adidas Helkin 3.0 Running shoes for men. The